{"type":null,"faqId":46234,"title":"什么是TalkBack？怎么打开？怎么关闭？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>TalkBack是给盲人和低视力用户使用的，启动触摸浏览后，原来的单击操作变成单击选中项目，在屏幕任意位置双击执行操作，比如要打开设置，可以先单击设置，然后在屏幕任意位置双击。滑动操作，需要两个手指按住屏幕滑动。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>可以通过点击设置-辅助功能-TalkBack，然后打开TalkBack的开关。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>关闭TalkBack时，需要先单击TalkBack开关，然后在屏幕任意位置双击，在弹出提示上单击确定，再双击，关闭TalkBack。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>注意：目前TalkBack不支持中文语音。当系统语言为英语时，打开TalkBack功能，操作时会有英文语音提示。当系统语言为中文时，打开TalkBack功能，操作只有提示音，没有语音。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2014","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444376341000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":42,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"盲人,视力不好,语音,盲人模式","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}